=You are given the following job requirements and a candidate's CV data.
Please evaluate the match and return a score from 1 to 100, along with a brief summary of your reasoning.

---

 Job Post Data:
- Job Title: {{ $json['Job Title'] }}
- Required Skills: {{ $json['Required Skills'].join(', ') }}
- Minimum Experience: {{ $json['Minimum Experience (Years)'] }} years
- Job Description: {{ $json['Job Description'] }}

---
 Applicant CV Data:
- Name: {{ $json.output.name }}
- Email: {{ $json.output.email }}
- Phone: {{ $json.output.phone }}
- Education: {{ $json.output.education }}
- Experience: {{ $json.output.experience_years }} years
- Skills: {{ $json.output.skills.join(', ') }}
- Last Position: {{ $json.output.last_position }}
- Last Company: {{ $json.output.last_company }}
- Language: {{ $json.output.language.join(', ') }}
- Certifications: {{ $json.output.certifications }}
